<Author>Secto9
<Content>From Hell to Heaven I think it resumes our thinking of barcelona's hotels.Hell, fake pictures, wrong location on website, long walk from car-park and personnal not really willing to take responsability for that. That麓s how starts our romantic holidays.We could not stand it and went looking for anything else, litteraly.Heaven, that's a Curious thing. Reception helpful and nice, at 2am the personnal made us a tour of the hotel to get away our suspicious mind, we were conquered with the great clean designed room they proposed, we enjoyed the variety of the included breakfast and had a good night sleep in a quiet area, even that close from Las Ramblas.The prices are a bit high, but it's personnal. We are more hostels travelers but after what we had, it was so good that we decided to go for it.For breakfast I like daylight and the dinning room of this hotel only has artificial light, but hey ! Even heaven is not perfect. Boy, if it is, means your dead !Hasta la vista, Curious!Sector9 
