<Author>weisertravels
<Content>Excellent hotel My husband and I recently stayed for 1 night after moving from another hotel in Barcelona. The hotel was very clean and had everything we needed. The bed was comfortable, although we opted to take the only room that was left which was a single room so it was tight, but our choice. The hotel is fairly new so it is very updated in both design including a television in the room with international channels and internet access in the lobby. The breakfast was good, with pastries, coffee, etc. The hotel is also in a great location just off of the busy La Rambla. We highly recommend this hotel to anyone traveling to Barcelona. 
